#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"> **amnesia**, *noun*:<br/>\n"
"> forgetfulness; loss of long-term memory.\n"
msgstr ""
"> **amnesia**, *名词*:<br/>\n"
"> 遗忘; 失去长期记忆.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"> **incognito**, *adjective & adverb*:<br/>\n"
"> (of a person) having one's true identity concealed.\n"
msgstr ""
"> **隐身**, *形容词*:<br/>\n"
"> 形容可以隐藏住自己真实身份的人。\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Tails is a live system that aims to preserve your privacy and anonymity. It "
"helps you to use the Internet anonymously and circumvent censorship almost "
"anywhere you go and on any computer but leaving no trace unless you ask it "
"to explicitly."
msgstr ""
"Tails "
"是旨在保护用户隐私和匿名性的自生操作系统。除用户刻意更改设定以外，它可以帮助用户在几乎任何地方用任何一部计算机匿名上网和绕开审查，且不会留下痕迹。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"It is a complete operating system designed to be used from a USB stick or a "
"DVD independently of the computer's original operating system. It is [[Free "
"Software|doc/about/license]] and based on [[Debian GNU/Linux|https://www."
"debian.org/]]."
msgstr ""
"Tails是一个完整的操作系统，您可以用 USB 记忆棒或 DVD 光碟进行操作，它会与原机操作系统独立分开。它是基于 [[Debian GNU/"
"Linux|https://www.debian.org/]] 的 [[免费软件|doc/about/license]]。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Tails comes with several built-in applications pre-configured with security "
"in mind: web browser, instant messaging client, email client, office suite, "
"image and sound editor, etc."
msgstr "Tails 提供了一些内置应用程序，如网页浏览器、即使通讯软件、电子邮箱软件、办公软件、图片和音频编辑器等，其原始设定皆以安全为优先。"

