msgstr "<a id=\"cryptography\"></a>\n"

#. type: Title =
#, no-wrap
msgid "State-of-the-art cryptographic tools\n"
msgstr "最先进的加密工具\n"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"Tails also comes with a selection of tools to protect your data using strong "
"encryption:"
msgstr "Tails 提供了多种使用强大加密技术的工具，以保护您的数据："

#. type: Bullet: '  - '
msgid ""
"[[Encrypt your USB sticks or external hard-disks|doc/encryption_and_privacy/"
"encrypted_volumes]] using <span class=\"definition\">[[!wikipedia "
"Linux_Unified_Key_Setup desc=\"LUKS\"]]</span>, the Linux standard for disk-"
"encryption."
msgstr ""
"通过<span class=\"definition\">[[!wikipedia Linux_Unified_Key_Setup desc=\""
"LUKS\"]]</span>，Linux 的磁盘加密标准，来[[加密 USB 记忆棒和外部硬盘|doc/encryption_and_privacy/"
"encrypted_volumes]]。"

#. type: Bullet: '  - '
msgid ""
"Automatically use HTTPS to encrypt all your communications to a number of "
"major websites using [HTTPS Everywhere](https://www.eff.org/https-"
"everywhere), a Firefox extension developed by the [Electronic Frontier "
"Foundation](https://www.eff.org)."
msgstr ""
"自动使用 [HTTPS Everywhere](https://www.eff.org/https-everywhere) 加密访问网页的连接。["
"HTTPS Everywhere](https://www.eff.org/https-everywhere) 是 Firefox 的扩展应用，其由 "
"[电子前锋基金会](https://www.eff.org) 所开发。"

#. type: Bullet: '  - '
msgid ""
"Encrypt and sign your emails and documents using the *de facto* standard "
"<span class=\"definition\">[[!wikipedia Pretty_Good_Privacy#OpenPGP desc="
"\"OpenPGP\"]]</span> either from Tails email client, text editor or file "
"browser."
msgstr ""
"无论在 Tails 电子邮箱，文本编辑器或是文件浏览器，使用*事实*标准<span class=\"definition\"> [[!wikipedia "
"Pretty_Good_Privacy#OpenPGP desc=\"OpenPGP\"]] </span>加密签发您的电子邮件和文档。"

#. type: Bullet: '  - '
msgid ""
"Protect your instant messaging conversations using <span class=\"definition"
"\">[[!wikipedia Off-the-Record_Messaging desc=\"OTR\"]]</span>, a "
"cryptographic tool that provides encryption, authentication and deniability."
msgstr ""
"使用可以加密、认证与否决的加密工具 <span class=\"definition\">[[!wikipedia Off-the-"
"Record_Messaging desc=\"OTR\"]]</span> 保护您在及时通讯工具中的交谈内容。"

#. type: Bullet: '  - '
msgid ""
"[[Securely delete your files|doc/encryption_and_privacy/secure_deletion]] "
"and clean your diskspace using [[Nautilus Wipe|http://wipetools.tuxfamily."
"org/nautilus-wipe.html]]."
msgstr ""
"[[安全删除您的文件|doc/encryption_and_privacy/secure_deletion]]并使过 [[Nautilus "
"Wipe|http://wipetools.tuxfamily.org/nautilus-wipe.html]] 清理磁盘。"

#. type: Plain text
msgid ""
"[[Read more about those tools in the documentation.|doc/"
"encryption_and_privacy]]"
msgstr "[[阅读文档以进一步了解这些工具。|doc/encryption_and_privacy]]"

